'''Muharramu''' (izina mu [[cyarabu]] : '''محرم''' ) ni ukwezi kwa mbere kuri [[karendari y’Ubuyisilamu]].  Abayisilamu b’isi yose bakirana uku kwezi ishavu ryinshi, bibuka Imamu Husseni umwuzukuru w’Intumwa Muhammadi.  Imamu Husseni intwari yatabarukiye itabaro ryo kurengera Ubuyisilamu no gutokombeza abasirikare ba Shitani.

Yaguye mu rugamba i [[Karbala]] yishwe n’ingabo za Yaziidi mwene Mu’awiya mwene Abu-Sufiyani nyuma yo kwanga kuyoboka ubutegetsi ruvumwa bw’ikirobezo Yaziidi

